                <p>Many Nintendo Switch games will be getting upgraded editions on the Switch 2. These new versions of old games will include new features using the Switch 2's hardware upgrades, like mouse controls, game chat, and cameras. They may also upgrade visuals and add new content.</p><p>Games set to get this upgrade include Metroid Prime 4, The Legend of Zelda: Breath of The Wild, Kirby and the Forgotten Land, and more.</p><p>Check out all the other announcements from the first <a href="https://www.gamespot.com/gallery/nintendo-direct-march-2025-all-the-biggest-announcements/2900-6377/" data-ref-id="2900-6377">Nintendo Switch 2 Direct</a> at the link. </p><p><em>This story is developing.</em></p>
  
                        
    
        
        
  
